{"tid":956464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【醫學研究】父母賺得多、地位高，兒女腦部發育更好","createTime":"2018-12-26T09:35:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T11:18:02.000Z","uid":202464,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a8b9a43e74f3004e52d9a6a3d92b32b879aefa64","tid":956464,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T09:35:10.000Z","msg":"今次研究再加入家長的社會經濟地位進一步比較。團隊發現家長社經地位越好，子女腦部兩個區域包括丘腦（Thalamus）及紋狀體（Striatum）都有明顯較佳的發展。丘腦是大腦中心一個關鍵的區域，專責傳遞及處理感官資訊，較大的丘腦容量與快速思考及語文智商有密切關係。"},{"pid":"60bf1a841b0a6138bb40fb74156c5192b089788e","tid":956464,"uid":83102,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T09:38:47.000Z","msg":"唔計dna啦<br />\n有錢老母比仔女食好營養價值野<br />\n冇錢個錢2,3歲開始食垃圾食物啦<br />\n你話邊個腦部發展好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69a212213f343cdfac7f8e1b4d01f72069fde52c","tid":956464,"uid":3302,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T09:41:30.000Z","msg":"公屋窮撚不願面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b4d143c6159e447ea60eed5e61b722eab70f5c1","tid":956464,"uid":29702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T09:42:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8258114412cba7432974300f9b3354b555d2ebda","tid":956464,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T09:44:06.000Z","msg":"大美人老公？"},{"pid":"4373ba3f9daef1663c5359a45f897c134cd9a20e","tid":956464,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T09:44:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"69d21e8260458ac3c04f5a78b9cecbe61b6a54dd","tid":956464,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T09:45:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大美人老公？</blockquote><br />\n許晉亨？"},{"pid":"603e14fc6755ece1724d4e0e4ed097da0900a8be","tid":956464,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T09:45:38.000Z","msg